1: <pb/><t>Al-layokab watx' k'anej bay Jehová, yujtol watx' is c'ul Cham jin, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
2: <t>Al-layokab watx' k'anej bay Cham Diosal masanil dioslak, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
3: <t>Al-layokab watx' k'anej bay Cham Yajawil eb yajaw, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
4: <t>Asannej Cham chi unen tzet yetal c'ayubtak yoqui, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
5: <t>A Cham max watx'nen satcan yuj is jelanil, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
6: <t>A Cham max litx'bantok tx'otx' tx'otx' ti' yibanlak aej, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
7: <t>A Cham max watx'nen c'u c'al xajaw, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
8: <t>Max watx'nej c'u yet chi tzektanej c'ualil, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
9: <t>Max watx'nej xajaw c'al waycan, yet chi tzektanej ak'balil, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
10: <t>A Cham max ak'on cam is babel unin junjun na yul yet Egipto, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
11: <t>A Cham max ion eltek eb israel yul yet Egipto tu', yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
12: <t>Max yion eltek eb yetok is miman yipalil, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
13: <t>A Cham max aon ay nan a' Cakyin Mar, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
14: <t>Cax max yion ec'tok eb israel nan a' mar tu', yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
15: <t>A Cham max aoncantok reyal Egipto c'al is soldado yul a' mar, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
16: <t>A Cham max ion bey is conob bay tz'inan tx'otx', yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
17: <t>A Cham max ak'on cam eb mimek rey, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
18: <t>Max yican el k'inal eb rey mimek yikbej, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal</t>
19: <t>A ton cham Sehón, reyal eb amorreo max ilay el k'inal tu', yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
20: <t>Yetok c'apax cham Og reyalil Basán max ilay el is k'inal, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
21: <t>Max pojlaytok is tx'otx' eb rey tu', yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
22: <t>Cax max yak'on Cham jun tx'otx' tu' is satakok Israel is chekbej, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
23: <t>A Cham max on naontek yet cannak on yalan, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
24: <t>Cax max on colc'al yul k'ab eb ajc'ul oc jin, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
25: <t>A Cham chi ak'on low anima c'al no no', yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal.</t>
26: <t>¡Al-layokab watx' k'anej bay Cham Diosal satcan, yujtol ayc'al is camc'ulal Cham yin tojbalk'inal!</t>
